<P>An <HI>Appendix,</HI> containing <HI>Remarks</HI> of an <HI>Ita|lian</HI> Gentleman, upon <HI>Switzerland,</HI> the <HI>Grison</HI> Country, the Bailiage of <HI>Lugane,</HI> the <HI>Lakes</HI> the Dutchey of <HI>Ferrara,</HI> the Estate of <HI>Bolognia</HI> the Country of the Great <HI>Duke</HI> of <HI>Tuscany,</HI> the temporal Government of the <HI>Pope,</HI> and the Re|duction of the Interest due by the <HI>Montes</HI> a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> <HI>Rome,</HI> and of the Avarice of the <HI>Iesuits</HI> and <HI>Priests p.</HI> 222, &amp;c.</P>
